<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #374151;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        background: white;
        padding: 30px;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-top: none;
      }
      .footer {
        background: #f9fafb;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-top: none;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #6b7280;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #10b981;
        color: white;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-weight: 500;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .success-box {
        background: #d1fae5;
        border-left: 4px solid #10b981;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .info-box {
        background: #f3f4f6;
        border-left: 4px solid #4f46e5;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>âœ… Payment Approved</h1>
      <p>Your billing setup has been approved</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Great news!</h2>
      
      <div class="success-box">
        <h3>Your billing setup has been approved</h3>
        <p>Your manual payment request for <strong><%= @organization.name %></strong> has been reviewed and approved by our team.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="info-box">
        <h3>What's Next?</h3>
        <p>You can now continue with your organization activation process. The next step is compliance setup.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Complete compliance requirements</li>
          <li>Sign necessary documents</li>
          <li>Finalize your organization activation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>To continue with your activation, please visit:</p>
      
      <a href="<%= tenant_activation_url %>" class="button">Continue Activation</a>
      
      <p>If you have any questions about the next steps, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message from HBS Data Processing System.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
